Adriana Sephora, Cherie DeVille, Jelena Jensen, Jenna Sativa, Kenna James, Kirsten Price, Pristine Edge, Vanessa Veracruz.

: The eighth volume of this popular, lesbian ass-worship series features curvy, Brazilian exchange student Adriana Sephora rents a guest house from prim and proper Cherie DeVille. Things get heated between them when Cherie dares to lecture young Adriana about her tendency to wear next to nothing around the neighborhood! Stunning Kirsten Price gets an earful after best pal, Jelena Jensen, finds out Kirsten is planning on getting butt implants. Jelena makes it her mission to show her best friend why implants aren't necessary. Uptight sorority president Vanessa Veracruz drives newcomer Kenna James crazy. Vanessa is super obsessive compulsive and Kenna has had enough. The two go head to head and then some! Finally, cute Jenna Sativa is excited to be recruited by a prestigious modeling agency, until the head of the agency, Pristine Edge, tells Jenna she needs to lose weight. Jenna attacks willowy Pristine with all her sassy curves, showing the agent who's boss!
